{
  "stem": "7093.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were rumors at the time also, at the beginning, that they put something into our food that we came, that we had menstruation, or that stopped the menstruation.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Not that we had menstruation, but that it stopped the menstruation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They never have been substantiated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I never could find anything about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then we-- so this was our food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now the, the soup we drank.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The cheese we ate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But there was this piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And you didn't have anything more until next day, the piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So you would have loved to keep it but of course you had no pockets.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You had nowhere where you could put it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You had nowhere where you could hide it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You knew if you dropped it or put it down somewhere somebody, one of your mates would straightaway take it and eat it without any conscience of guilt because they were also hungry.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when people are hungry, most people they just take.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And-- so I-- so usually we ate it up because-- and then we had absolutely nothing more.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't a large piece anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But one would have loved to keep it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then in the evening we were again put in into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that was a day gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And that's how it went on with that one interruption until, I think, the 1st of August.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We arrived in Auschwitz on the 7th of July, and I think it was the 1st of August that there was this big selection, when not only us-- Oh, there was one incident in before, which I want to tell.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "One day-- oh, that was also the first of August.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
